title: Annual median salary in financial , insurance and real estate services in the UK 2019
summary: This bar chart has 5 columns on the x axis representing Service In Uk, and Median annual salary in GBP in each Service In Uk on the y axis.
The Median annual salary in GBP is appeared to be the highest at Service In Uk Financial services activities and lowest at Service In Uk Real estate.
The maximum Service In Uk Financial services activities has got 1.62 times higher Median annual salary in GBP than the minimum Service In Uk Real estate.
